# Copy to `.env` and fill in locally (never commit `.env`).
#   cp .env.example .env
#
# See `README.md` (GitHub PAT) and `SECURITY.md`.

# GitHub Personal Access Token — optional but required for automations that upload
# invoice PDFs to TrueSightDAO/.github `assets/` (Contribution Ledger workflow) or for
# `gh` CLI with `GH_TOKEN` if your token includes pull request scopes.
# Create at: https://github.com/settings/tokens (classic: repo scope for private needs;
# fine-grained: Contents read/write on TrueSightDAO/.github; add Pull requests read/write
# if you use this token for `gh pr create` / merge).
GITHUB_PAT=
